Original repository: https://github.com/jerryfeng2003/PointGST
Paper: "Parameter-Efficient Fine-Tuning in Spectral Domain for
       Point Cloud Learning", IEEE TPAMI

This is a derivative work adapted for the LIDARLearn library.
Changes from the original:
  - Integrated into the LIDARLearn model registry and config system
  - Split into PointGST (PointMAE backbone) and PointGPT_GST (PointGPT backbone)
  - Uses BasePointCloudModel base class
  - Adapted constructor to accept config objects
